column2: "What's wrong, child? You can't kill me if you don't attack..."
"How horrible! You really attacked your friends, you monster."
"Stop this! I am a guardian, not a murderer!"
"That impertinent gaze. It's too early to kill you just yet!"
"I'll have you in the pit of despair before you die, child!"
"Stop... don't do it... don't kill them...!"
"I'm... I'm a guardian of the people... I must protect everyone!"
"Who am I risking my life for in the first place...?"
